OL,3,CAirlines cut two million seats: How
OL,4,Cwill this affect summer travel plans?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News' Akshay Raja
OL,8,FGlobal airlines have cut two million
OL,9,Fseats from their May schedules amid
OL,10,Fdisruptions to global fuel supplies.
OL,12,FAccording to data from aviation
OL,13,Fanalytics firm Cirium, there were over
OL,14,F132 million scheduled seats for
OL,15,Finternational flights in May on April
OL,16,F10.
OL,18,FBy April 21, this had fallen to 130
OL,19,Fmillion seats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
