OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778054737
OL,3,CAirlines cut two million seats: How
OL,4,Cwill this affect summer travel plans?
OL,6,FOver the same period, the number of
OL,7,Fplanned flights fell by over 13,000.
OL,9,FThe reduction in capacity comes as
OL,10,Fshipping traffic through the Strait of
OL,11,FHormuz remains blocked, and vessels
OL,12,Fare prevented from travelling through
OL,13,Fthe passage.
OL,15,FA fifth of global oil and gas supplies
OL,16,Fare typically transported through the
OL,17,FStrait. With the movement of these
OL,18,Fvessels disrupted, oil prices are
OL,19,Fsurging and airlines are facing higher
OL,20,Foperating costs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
