OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778054737
OL,3,CAirlines cut two million seats: How
OL,4,Cwill this affect summer travel plans?
OL,6,FEuropean jet fuel prices more than
OL,7,Fdoubled over six weeks from late
OL,8,FFebruary, according to Cirium.
OL,10,FThe head of the International Energy
OL,11,FAgency, Faith Birol, warned in April
OL,12,Fthat this is the "largest energy
OL,13,Fcrisis we have ever faced", suggesting
OL,14,FEurope has only around six weeks of
OL,15,Fjet fuel left.
OL,17,FFor airlines, this means flight
OL,18,Fcancellations or complete closure in
OL,19,Fsome cases.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
