OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778054737
OL,3,CAirlines cut two million seats: How
OL,4,Cwill this affect summer travel plans?
OL,6,FWith May half-term and summer holidays
OL,7,Fapproaching, could this affect your
OL,8,Ftravel plans?
OL,10,FHow have airlines responded?
OL,12,FGermany's Lufthansa cancelled 20,000
OL,13,Fshort-haul flights from its schedule
OL,14,Funtil October, due to the sharp price
OL,15,Fincreases.
OL,17,FThey say ticket prices may continue to
OL,18,Fincrease given the current
OL,19,Fgeopolitical environment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
