CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778054737
OL,3,CAirlines cut two million seats: How
OL,4,Cwill this affect summer travel plans?
OL,6,FBritish Airways has paused the
OL,7,Fmajority of its flights to parts of
OL,8,Fthe Middle East until at least June
OL,9,F,while all flights to Amman, Bahrain,
OL,10,FDubai, and Tel Aviv are temporarily
OL,11,Fcancelled until May 31. BA's Abu Dhabi
OL,12,Fflights remain cancelled until October.
OL,14,FBut other airlines suggest it is
OL,15,Fbusiness as usual.
OL,17,FEasyJet says it is not seeing any
OL,18,Fdisruption to fuel supply and will
OL,19,Fcontinue to operate flights as normal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
