CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778054737
OL,3,CAirlines cut two million seats: How
OL,4,Cwill this affect summer travel plans?
OL,6,FWill this disrupt holiday plans?
OL,8,FHoliday plans should not be affected
OL,9,Fon the whole, according to experts.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News, they made a key
OL,12,Fdistinction between the cost of fuel
OL,13,Fand fuel shortages.
OL,15,FThey emphasise that there have been
OL,16,Fvery few flight cancellations in the
OL,17,FUK and Europe, and those cancellations
OL,18,Fwhich have been made are due to the
OL,19,Frising cost of jet fuel rather than
OL,20,Fshortages.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
