OL,3,CAirlines cut two million seats: How
OL,4,Cwill this affect summer travel plans?
OL,6,FRory Boland, Travel Editor at Which?
OL,7,Fhighlights that Lufthansa's
OL,8,Fcancellation of flights was because
OL,9,Fthe airline decided it was too
OL,10,Fexpensive to run these flights.
OL,12,FBoland says airlines will cancel
OL,13,Fflights while prices remain high, but
OL,14,Fthese will be for routes with multiple
OL,15,Fflights a day, so passengers can be
OL,16,Frebooked.
OL,18,FHe predicts that most flights in
OL,19,FEurope this summer will continue as
OL,20,Fnormal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
