OL,3,CAirlines cut two million seats: How
OL,4,Cwill this affect summer travel plans?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FABTA, the trade association for tour
OL,12,Foperators and travel agents in the UK,
OL,13,Freiterate this point.
OL,15,FIn a statement, the organisation said
OL,16,Fthat the government's announcement "is
OL,17,Fa precautionary measure", rather than
OL,18,Fan emergency one.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
