OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778054737
OL,3,CAirlines cut two million seats: How
OL,4,Cwill this affect summer travel plans?
OL,6,FThe organisation says that where
OL,7,Fchanges do occur, "passengers are
OL,8,Flikely to still travel on the same day
OL,9,Fand avoid last-minute disruption."
OL,11,FWhat has the government said?
OL,13,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,14,Fhas assured customers their summer
OL,15,Fholiday plans will not be disrupted
OL,16,Fdue to fuel shortages.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
