OL,3,CAirlines cut two million seats: How
OL,4,Cwill this affect summer travel plans?
OL,6,FAsked if people jetting off abroad are
OL,7,Flikely to face problems this summer,
OL,8,FMs Alexander told Sky News' Sunday
OL,9,FMorning With Trevor Phillips: "I've
OL,10,Fspent every week of the last two
OL,11,Fmonths in close contact with airlines
OL,12,Fand airports.
OL,14,F"On Thursday of this week, airlines
OL,15,Ftold me very clearly that they have
OL,16,Fgood visibility over the next six to
OL,17,Feight weeks of jet fuel supply.
OL,19,F"There is no current disruption to jet
OL,20,Ffuel supplies."
