OL,3,CAirlines cut two million seats: How
OL,4,Cwill this affect summer travel plans?
OL,6,FThe government has introduced a
OL,7,Ftemporary rule which allows airlines
OL,8,Fto group passengers from different
OL,9,Fflights together onto fewer planes, to
OL,10,Fsave fuel.
OL,12,FThis means passengers could be moved
OL,13,Ffrom the service they originally
OL,14,Fbooked to a similar one.
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
